### ===============================
### /items/  (Query + Validación String)
### ===============================

### ✅ OK: sin query (q es opcional)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/items/
Accept: application/json


### ✅ OK: q válido (>= 3 caracteres)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/items/?q=hola
Accept: application/json


### ❌ 422: q demasiado corto (min_length=3)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/items/?q=ab
Accept: application/json


### ❌ 422: q demasiado largo (max_length=50)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/items/?q=abcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyzabcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyzabc
Accept: application/json


